Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:48.65,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The creatures you know \Nof no longer exist here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.57,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,400)}Silver Soul Arc
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:52.79,Main,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,creature who fears humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:53.91,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(190,1)}The Creatures Known as Humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:57.66,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,Utsuro has lived an endless life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:57.66,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,and he brings about endless death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:24:04.25,Side Bar Top,TextR,0000,0000,0000,,With the end of the world approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:24:04.25,Side Bar Bottom,TextL,0000,0000,0000,,people choose to burn their \Nflame of life bright and strong!